sub_title: Kindergarten and Early Years Educator | Special Needs Educator | Childcare Practitioner
summary:
• I am a Teacher with over 5 years of experience in Early Childhood Education. I graduated with a diploma in Special Needs Education and gained wide international teaching background by working in kindergartens in Brazil and Hungary. 
• With strong interpersonal skills I am a flexible person described as a committed, reliable coworker. I am enthusiastic about working in a multicultural, diverse environment and connecting with people from all over the world. Besides education, I am passionate about maternity and birth support and I attend a doula course.
